title: Jazz Resto e Burgers
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Offers 4 vegan burgers: Mushroom, chickpea, falafel and corn. Also has fries with vegan cheese and bacon. A couple of vegan desserts are available, as well as a chocolate and peanut butter milkshake with coconut whipped cream. Dishes are named after jazz greats. Has live music. Some staff speak English. Close to Metro Ana Rosa.
